resources.name: Detailed information on public opinion website

description:
This special Eurobarometer was carried out between 22 September and 3 November 2007, in the twenty-seven European Union Member States.
This Eurobarometer was commissioned by the Directorate-General Communication of the European Commission on behalf of the European Parliament.
1. We shall start with awareness regarding the European Parliament.
2. The second part is devoted to opinions on the European Parliament’s place and actions.
3. The third part is devoted to the subjective image of the European Parliament.
4. The fourth and last part of our analysis is devoted to the European Parliament’s role,

#####The results by volumes are distributed as follows:
* Volume A: Countries
* Volume AA: Groups of countries
* Volume A' (AP): Trends
* Volume AA' (AAP): Trends of groups of countries
* Volume B: EU/socio-demographics
* Volume C: Country/socio-demographics
title: Special Eurobarometer 288: The European Parliament
name: S1463_68_1_288
